data.description: Nestled in the charming town of Gentry, this beautifully maintained home features 4 bedrooms & 2 bathrooms, providing a comfortable & inviting living space. The open-concept design effortlessly blends modern convenience with timeless appeal. The spacious kitchen, with a large island & ample cabinetry, boasts perfect for entertaining. Enjoy serene moments in the well appointed backyard, ideal for outdoor gatherings. With its convenient location near Main Street, Gentry Community Park, & Eagle Watch Nature Trail, this home offers both comfort & convenience. Don't miss the opportunity to make this lovely property yours & experience the best of Gentry living. Schedule a showing today!
